Subject: Retro Games: Better than New
Description: There has been a huge influx of interest in classic games. From Barcades to stores selling Retro Games, why, in a world of PS4s and XBox Ones, are we suddenly obsessed with Atari 2600s and Nintendo Entertainment Systems? What can modern game makers learn from our continued love of more simple games?  Speakers include:Angie Rush, Brittany Burke, Britain Woodman - Track: Videogaming  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none

Subject: Retro Gaming: Come Play!
Description: Come relive your youth as you play away the hours on a collection of retro gaming systems, including Atari 2600, NES, SNES and many others.   Speakers include:Angie Rush, Brittany Burke, Chris Roland - Track: Videogaming  - Duration: 5 hours and 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
